  "text": "To summarise, these findings have demonstrated the challenging learning journey associated with failure. To use the words of [CITATION_1] , the participants have learned essential lessons about entrepreneurship -the hard way‖. I now move onto consider the theoretical and policy implications of the study and areas for further research.",
